<h2>Navigation</h2>

<p>The links on the upper left side of this page are primarily concerned with my music and career.</p>

<p>It features a biography, music samples, a section on my Dad, "The Silver Fox". The road section features information about recent or upcoming shows. There's a merchandise section, where you can buy CDs, and photos. There's also a full length video section, a guestbook area, and finally a weblog, which I try to update frequently.</p>

<p>I will also be addressing some of the questions that I'm often asked during my travels. So, with that in mind, enjoy the site and carry on...<br />
 $CRjr</p>
