<div id="main">
<h2>WELCOME..</h2>

<p><img class="imgleft" src="crjr.jpg" width="228" height="293" alt="Charlie Rich Jr." /></p>

<p>I'm delighted that you've made your way to my site. My name is Charlie Rich, Jr. I've been a professional song 
writer, entertainer, and keyboard player most of my life. I pretty much grew up in the music industry, as my mother and father were involved in music since the 1950s. My father achieved legendary status as a musician's musician, a singer's singer and a world class entertainer.
</p>
<p>My mother made her reputation as a successful song writer and publisher, not to mention being my father's biggest inspiration. Charlie Rich (Sr.), known to many as "The Silver Fox", achieved a string of hits such as "Behind Closed Doors", "The Most Beautiful Girl In The World", "A Very Special Love Song" and many more.</p>

<p>He started his musical career at SUN Studio in the late 50s as a piano player/singer. He then went on to become one of country music's biggest stars of all time, while managing to "cross over" and have success on the Pop charts as well. I feel that the reason he could appeal to a varied fan base so successfully is that he loved all types of music. He didn't just stick to one style, but succeeded in displaying artistry in a variety of musical genres. His music struck a chord with people from all over the world, sans stylistic boundaries. I too have a great appreciation for that same musical ideal. In other words, it's all good.</p>

