<h2 style="font-size:150%">Hemsby 59 Rock n' Roll Show, Oct. Friday 6th to Monday 9th, 2017</h2>

<p><a href="http://www.hemsbyrocknroll.co.uk/events.html" title="Hemsby 59 Rock n' Roll Show, Oct. Friday 6th to Monday 9th, 2017"><img style="float:left; margin:13px;" src="images/hemsby-th300.png" width="216" height="300" alt="Hemsby 59"></a> THANK YOU HEMSBY ! ! ! What a wonderful time. Everything I had been told was true. The audience was simply unbelievable and we were thrilled to meet so many wonderful rockabilly fans. It was one of the rocking-est shows on the planet. What an honor to be a part of this legendary party&mdash;the longest running Rockabilly Weekender in Europe. </p>

